      "review_summary": "The branch threads plugin install records through runtime plugin loading and manifest registry trust checks for diagnostics-otel, with regression coverage for trusted persisted installs and spoofed or untrusted records.\n\nPR surface: Source +34, Tests +504. Total +538 across 8 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source inspection: service startup only injects `internalDiagnostics` when the manifest record has `trustedOfficialInstall`, and diagnostics-otel returns early when that capability is absent. I did not run a live Gateway/OTEL setup in this read-only review.",
